sequenceDiagram
    participant Build as Build System<br/>(Konflux)
    participant Init as Init Container<br/>pipelines-components
    participant Volume as Shared Volume<br/>/config/managed-pipelines
    participant KFPAPI as KFP API Server
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow<br/>Engine
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LS as LlamaStack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/S
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PVC as PVC Workspace

    Note over Build,Init: Flow 1: Managed Pipeline Staging
    Build->>Init: Bundle compiled pipeline YAMLs<br/>+ managed-pipelines.json
    Init->>Init: Read managed-pipelines.json
    Init->>Volume: Copy pipeline YAMLs<br/>(shutil.copy2, path-escape validation)
    Volume-->>KFPAPI: Volume mount discovery<br/>registers managed pipelines

    Note over KFPAPI,PVC: Flow 2: AutoML Tabular Training
    KFPAPI->>Argo: Schedule pipeline run
    Argo->>S3: automl_data_loader<br/>Download dataset<br/>AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>Argo: Dataset files
    Argo->>PVC: Store training data
    PVC-->>Argo: Read train data
    Argo->>Argo: autogluon_models_training<br/>(odh-automl image)
    Argo->>PVC: Write model artifacts
    Argo->>KFPAPI: Leaderboard evaluation<br/>KFP artifact API

    Note over KFPAPI,PVC: Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization
    KFPAPI->>Argo: Schedule pipeline run
    Argo->>S3: documents_discovery<br/>List S3 objects<br/>AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>Argo: Document list
    Argo->>S3: text_extraction<br/>Download documents<br/>AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>Argo: Document files
    Argo->>LS: search_space_preparation<br/>API key auth
    LS-->>Argo: Search space config
    Argo->>LS: rag_templates_optimization<br/>Embedding + generation<br/>API key auth
    LS-->>Argo: Optimized RAG patterns
    Argo->>LS: documents_indexing<br/>Vector store write<br/>API key auth
    LS-->>Argo: Index confirmation

    Note over KFPAPI,PVC: Flow 4: Fine-tuning (LoRA/OSFT/SFT)
    KFPAPI->>Argo: Schedule pipeline run
    Argo->>HF: dataset_download<br/>HF_TOKEN (optional)
    HF-->>Argo: Dataset
    Argo->>K8sAPI: train_model<br/>Create TrainJob CR<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Argo: TrainJob created
    K8sAPI->>HF: Worker pods download model<br/>HF_TOKEN
    HF-->>K8sAPI: Model weights
    K8sAPI->>PVC: Write checkpoints + model
    PVC-->>Argo: Load model for evaluation
    Argo->>Argo: universal_llm_evaluator<br/>(vLLM + lm-eval in-process)
    Argo->>MR: kubeflow_model_registry<br/>Register model metadata<br/>HTTP (insecure)
    MR-->>Argo: Registration confirmed
